des: Nestled amidst 83 acres of breathtaking North Atlanta landscapes, our restaurant boasts contemporary charm, Italian-inspired cuisine, and elegant dining spaces for gatherings and events. We are just 20 minutes from Buckhead and 11 minutes from Dunwoody, Georgia. Villa Christina is your gateway to stylish indulgence.
